<h4 id="noise_abetement_procedures">Noise Abetement Procedures</h4>
<div class="level4">
<ul>
<li class="level1"><div class="li"> When take-off on RWY 01 with a clearance to turn right, the ACFT must maintain the RWY axis until 3000 ft before beginning right turn.</div>
</li>
<li class="level1"><div class="li"> When take-off on RWY 19 with a clearance to turn right, the ACFT must maintain the RWY axis during 3 minutes before beginning right turn.</div>
</li>
</ul>
<hr />

